Minnie V. TAFT et al. v. MUTUAL LIFE INSURANCE COMPANY OF NEW YORK. No. 1016. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Jan. 10, 1934. M. M. Thomas, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellants. Embry, Johnson, Crowe & Tolbert, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, PHILLIPS, and Me-' DERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed for failure to prosecute.
